org.raistlic.common.reflection

Class ReflectionPredicates

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.raistlic.common.reflection.ReflectionPredicates

  • public final class ReflectionPredicates
extends java.lang.Object
    The class holds a collections of static factory methods that export different types of Predicate implementations for the reflection utility types.
